{"data":[{"date":"08:48 06/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 06/08: L\u1ed9 l\u00fd do Mina l\u1eadt m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/5/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-0608-lo-ly-do-mina-lat-mat-voi-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 06/08.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1ed9 l\u00fd do Mina l\u1eadt m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi MU</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 0608 L\u1ed9 l\u00fd do Mina l\u1eadt m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 0608 L\u1ed9 l\u00fd do Mina l\u1eadt m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/27/Diem-tin-bong-da-sang-0608-Lo-ly-do-Mina-lat-mat-voi-MU-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Yerry Mina t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo The Sun, M.U \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1ee5 Mina. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Mina, Felipe Russo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi M.U, nh\u01b0ng sau \u0111\u00f3 \u00f4ng n\u00e0y thay \u0111\u1ed5i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1edfi kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n ph\u1ee5, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea3 ti\u1ec1n cho Yerry Mina v\u00e0 m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Klopp ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Liverpool v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mua th\u00eam c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Klopp kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u1ebfu chia tay m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u00e1i t\u00ean trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi \u00f4ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n mua th\u00eam \u00edt nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1eefa, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ch\u1eb7n chi\u1ec1u mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Willian: &quot;T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 r\u1eddi Chelsea \u0111\u1ebfn MU ho\u1eb7c Real n\u1ebfu...&quot;</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Willian n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea thay v\u00ec \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho M.U hay Real \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. Ng\u00f4i sao 29 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu Chelsea mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n anh.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/willian-mot-lan-nua-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-172-193826.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/23/willian-mot-lan-nua-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/willian-mot-lan-nua-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-172-193826.html\">Willian: T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 r\u1eddi Chelsea \u0111\u1ebfn MU ho\u1eb7c Real n\u1ebfu...</span><br>\r\nWillian n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea thay v\u00ec \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho M.U hay Real \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. Ng\u00f4i sao 29 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Mourinho mu\u1ed1n M.U ph\u00e1 k\u00e9t mua th\u00eam ng\u00f4i sao</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jose Mourinho cong khai to thai do khong hai long voi cong tac chuyen nhuong cho Ed Woodward dam nhiem.\" title=\"Jose Mourinho c\u00f4ng khai t\u1ecf th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Ed Woodward \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/mourinho-dang-rat-khong-on-o-man-united.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jose Mourinho mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bayern Munich, HLV Jose Mourinho kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh M.U ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea1nh tranh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Pep Guardiola ch\u1ec9 ra hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau C\u00fap</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha d\u00e0nh th\u1eddi gian ca ng\u1ee3i Sergio Aguero v\u00e0 Bernardo Silva sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a Man City tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ch\u01a1i m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t, Barkley v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Sarri b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 ch\u01a1i m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City trong tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, nh\u01b0ng HLV Sarri \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khen ng\u1ee3i t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Barkley v\u00e0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng anh s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Chelsea trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/choi-mo-nhat-barkley-van-duoc-hlv-sarri-bao-ke-172-193816.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/choi-mo-nhat-barkley-van-duoc-hlv-sarri-bao-ke.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/choi-mo-nhat-barkley-van-duoc-hlv-sarri-bao-ke-172-193816.html\">Ch\u01a1i m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t, Barkley v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Sarri b\u1ea3o k\u00ea</span><br>\r\nHLV Sarri \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khen ng\u1ee3i t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Barkley v\u00e0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng anh s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Chelsea trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>T\u00e2n HLV Sarri n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u00f9ng Chelsea?</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Sarri\" title=\"HLV Sarri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/hlv-maurizio-sarri-du-am-tran-chelsea-vs-man-city-sieu-cup-anh-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Sarri t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City trong tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, HLV Sarri kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng Man xanh qu\u00e1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc. C\u1ef1u HLV Napoli kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Fulham h\u1ecfi m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Arsenal</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Daily Mail, Fulham \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch h\u1ecfi m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Calum Chambers c\u1ee7a Arsenal, song kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao. HLV Unai Emery \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u0111a n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef anh \u1edf l\u1ea1i Emirates.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5133","checkdouble":"193832"},{"date":"07:48 06/08","title":"H\u00e0ng hot World Cup ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \"th\u1ea3 th\u00ednh\" Man Utd","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/23/hang-hot-world-cup-tiep-tuc-tha-thinh-man-utd.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ivan Rakitic ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 nguy\u1ec7n v\u1ecdng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng Premier League khi th\u1eddi gian ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec9nh cao kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 29.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch \u00e1 qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018 c\u1ee7a Croatia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00f3p s\u1ee9c r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn b\u1edfi Ivan Rakitic, ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quan tr\u1ecdng trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u00e0 chung k\u1ebft. Nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh 29 tu\u1ed5i tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn Man Utd th\u00e8m mu\u1ed1n anh, sau n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng b\u1edfi th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3 b\u1ebf t\u1eafc v\u1edbi Inter Milan.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Perisic c\u1ee7a Inter Milan \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Perisic c\u1ee7a Inter Milan \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/hang-hot-world-cup-tiep-tuc-tha-thinh-man-utd.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Perisic c\u1ee7a Inter Milan</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y nh\u1ea5t, Perisic l\u1ea1i khi\u1ebfn Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee9ng ng\u1ed3i kh\u00f4ng y\u00ean v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u mang t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t &ldquo;th\u1ea3 th\u00ednh&rdquo; c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 n\u1ed9i dung mu\u1ed1n chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao Croatia: &ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 29 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec9nh cao n\u1eefa. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady m\u00e0 n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1eed s\u1ee9c \u1edf nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn kh\u00e1c, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng n\u1eafm b\u1eaft cho b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110\u00fang v\u1eady, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gia nh\u1eadp Premier League n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh hay La Liga c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o ri\u00eang m\u00ecnh b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o mong mu\u1ed1n s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, h\u1ecd bi\u1ebft s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm t\u00f4i \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u v\u00e0 l\u00e0m g\u00ec r\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea5y.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda t\u1ea1i Anh v\u00e0o h\u1ebft ng\u00e0y th\u1ee9 n\u0103m 9/8 trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a th\u1eddi gian kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u cho Man Utd h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u01b0u ti\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7, v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t trong ba c\u00e1i t\u00ean Toby Alderweireld, Harry Maguire v\u00e0 Yerry Mina c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Old Trafford v\u00e0o gi\u1edd ch\u00f3t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tien-ve-ivan-perisic-dat-xat-ra-mieng-cho-mu-172-164447.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/7/21/tin-nong-chuyen-nhuong-ngay-247-inter-milan-san-sang-ban-ivan-perisic-cho-mu-neu-.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tien-ve-ivan-perisic-dat-xat-ra-mieng-cho-mu-172-164447.html\">Ivan Perisic: \u0110\u1eaft x\u1eaft ra mi\u1ebfng cho Man Utd</span><br>\r\n48 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 28 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a ph\u00fat gi\u00e2y n\u00e0o th\u1eed l\u1eeda \u1edf Premier League, \u0111\u00f3 hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t canh b\u1ea1c. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia &ndash;...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5132","checkdouble":"193822"},{"date":"07:58 06/08","title":"Willian: \"T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 r\u1eddi Chelsea \u0111\u1ebfn MU ho\u1eb7c Real n\u1ebfu...\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/23/willian-mot-lan-nua-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Willian n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea thay v\u00ec \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho M.U hay Real \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. Ng\u00f4i sao 29 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu Chelsea mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n anh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Willian \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Conte tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng song Willian v\u1eabn ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t. Anh c\u00f3 7 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 6 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o sau 20 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00e1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Willian n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ebfn MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Willian n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ebfn MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/11/Willian-noi-ve-tuong-lai-truoc-tin-don-den-MU-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Willian \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Willian khi\u1ebfn anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m. Barca 3 l\u1ea7n h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0a ra kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn Chelsea h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau khi Barca b\u1ecf cu\u1ed9c, M.U v\u00e0 Real Madrid \u0111ang l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ea1nh tranh ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 29 tu\u1ed5i. Mourinho r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 \u1edf s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Willian.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/co-hay-khong-viec-real-chi-70-trieu-bang-mua-willian-180-192421.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real Madrid c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi \u0111\u1eadm mua Willian</span>, Don Balon kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a TBN ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. HLV Sarri \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp trung mu\u1ed9n, \u00f4ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Willian n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Willian l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Willian n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea thay v\u00ec \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho M.U hay Real \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Willian T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 r\u1eddi Chelsea \u0111\u1ebfn MU ho\u1eb7c Real n\u1ebfu h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Willian T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 r\u1eddi Chelsea \u0111\u1ebfn MU ho\u1eb7c Real n\u1ebfu h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/11/Willian-Toi-chi-roi-Chelsea-den-MU-hoac-Real-neu-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Willian tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Trong nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf. \u01afu ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd bi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 ng\u00e0y mai. D\u00f9 sao th\u00ec t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i lu\u00f4n lu\u00f4n c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t vui khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea, ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o t\u00f4i n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi CLB. N\u1ebfu t\u00f4i c\u00f3 r\u1eddi Stamford Bridge th\u00ec ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t l\u00fd do, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 CLB mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n t\u00f4i m\u00e0 th\u00f4i&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;\u0110\u00f4i khi t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i v\u1eabn chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, b\u00e2y gi\u1edd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chu k\u1ef3 m\u1edbi. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi HLV m\u1edbi, hy v\u1ecdng m\u00f9a t\u1edbi s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi Chelsea&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5131","checkdouble":"193826"},{"date":"08:14 06/08","title":"C\u1ef1c n\u00f3ng: Yerry Mina t\u1edbi Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/8/cuc-nong-yerry-mina-toi-ngoai-hang-anh-nhung-khong-phai-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Yerry Mina t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i MU \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Everton, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Sport c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Goodison Park \u0111ang \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 28 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M.U b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd nh\u1eadn tr\u00e1i \u0111\u1eafng v\u1ee5 Mina</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, M.U \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barca. Mourinho c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u1ea5t ng\u1edd Yerry Mina t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i MU \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Everton h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"B\u1ea5t ng\u1edd Yerry Mina t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i MU \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Everton h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/27/Bat-ngo-Yerry-Mina-tu-choi-MU-de-cap-ben-Everton-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Yerry Mina b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd kh\u00f4ng t\u1edbi M.U \u1edf ph\u00fat ch\u00f3t</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Barca, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-ca-nhan-voi-mina-172-193764.html\" target=\"_blank\">M.U \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi Mina</span>. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994, t\u1ea1i Old Trafford ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i nh\u1eadn l\u01b0\u01a1ng 145.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Barca, h\u1ecd thu v\u1ec1 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Nh\u1eefng t\u01b0\u1edfng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra \u00eam \u0111\u1eb9p th\u00ec \u1edf nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng M.U l\u1ea1i b\u1ecb c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia l\u1eadt m\u1eb7t. Theo The Sun, M.U \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1ee5 Mina.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Mina, Felipe Russo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi M.U, nh\u01b0ng sau \u0111\u00f3 \u00f4ng n\u00e0y thay \u0111\u1ed5i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1edfi kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n ph\u1ee5, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea3 ti\u1ec1n cho Yerry Mina v\u00e0 m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Mina s\u1eafp c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Everton</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Yerry Mina t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i MU \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Everton, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Sport c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Goodison Park \u0111ang \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 28 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"yerry mina Barcelona\" title=\"yerry mina Barcelona\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/cuc-nong-yerry-mina-toi-ngoai-hang-anh-nhung-khong-phai-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Yerry Mina s\u1eafp l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Everton Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng MU,</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Felipe Russo c\u1ee7a Mina thay v\u00ec t\u1edbi Manchester \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi M.U th\u00ec l\u1ea1i bay t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i b\u1ea3n doanh c\u1ee7a Everton \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSport kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p, Mina g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. \u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i, Everton \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i chi ra 28 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Barca, M.U s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd d\u1ed3n to\u00e0n l\u1ef1c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Harry Maguire c\u1ee7a Leicester ho\u1eb7c Toby Alderweireld c\u1ee7a Tottenham.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi m\u00e0 TTCN \u0111i v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng M.U chi \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t trong hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5130","checkdouble":"193827"},{"date":"19:35 05/08","title":"Sao 120 tri\u1ec7u Euro n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c M.U v\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/5/milinkovicsavic-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sergej Milinkovic-Savic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Lazio kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111ang r\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Milinkovic-Savic l\u00e0 \u201ch\u00e0ng hot\u201d</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 v\u1eeba qua ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn phong \u0111\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Sergej Milinkovic-Savic t\u1ea1i Lazio. C\u1ef1u th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Genk \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p t\u1edbi 12 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng (nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9 2 trong \u0111\u1ed9i) v\u00e0 3 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7t danh \u201c\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edbi World Cup 2018, d\u00f9 Serbia b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay sau v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, Milinkovic-Savic v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. S\u1ee9c n\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 23 tu\u1ed5i tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u0169ng v\u00ec th\u1ebf c\u00e0ng d\u00e2ng cao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sergej Milinkovic-Savic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sergej Milinkovic-Savic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/milinkovicsavic-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Milinkovic-Savic \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi m\u1eddi ch\u00e0o</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng Manchester United, Chelsea (Anh), Inter Milan, AC Milan (Italia) \u0111\u1ec1u d\u00e0nh cho Milinkovic-Savic s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t. V\u1edbi Milan, h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u00ean t\u1edbi 120 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed9ng \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>T\u1eadp trung t\u1ea1i Lazio</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMilinkovic-Savic m\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng Lazio sau k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u1eadu World Cup 2018. Anh c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho Biancocelesti tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi Arsenal t\u1ea1i Stockholm (Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n) h\u00f4m qua theo gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. B\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eefng suy \u0111o\u00e1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Lazio.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sergej Milinkovic-Savic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sergej Milinkovic-Savic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/AC-Milan-muon-mua-Sergej-Milinkovic-Savic-cua-Lazio-voi-gia-khung-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Milinkovic-Savic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 b\u00ecnh th\u1ea3n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Lazio v\u00e0 c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi CLB (\u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2021). T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra. Nh\u01b0ng trong \u0111\u1ea7u t\u00f4i l\u00fac n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Lazio v\u00e0 t\u1eadp trung c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng\u201d, Milinkovic-Savic n\u00f3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nJuventus m\u00f9a n\u00e0y th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tham v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn. H\u1ecd c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u1edbi \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro Cristiano Ronaldo. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Milinkovic-Savic kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 lo ng\u1ea1i cho Lazio, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i. \u201c\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi cho Serie A b\u1edfi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thu h\u00fat c\u00e1c t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i kh\u00e1c. S\u1ebd c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u1eafc nghi\u1ec7t h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i.\u201d<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Serie A tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/inter-quyet-tam-chieu-mo-bang-duoc-luka-modric-176-193748.html\">Inter quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Luka Modric</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/leonardo-bonucci-khong-xin-loi-sau-khi-tro-lai-juventus-176-193737.html\">Leonardo Bonucci quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng xin l\u1ed7i sau khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/gattuso-chang-cau-thu-nao-co-the-tu-choi-chung-toi-176-193717.html\">Gattuso: Ch\u1eb3ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i ch\u00fang t\u00f4i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/goc-nhin-tai-hop-cuu-den-juventus-kho-lam-nen-chuyen-o-champions-league-176-193654.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: T\u00e1i h\u1ee3p \u201cc\u1eebu \u0111en\u201d, Juventus kh\u00f3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n \u1edf Champions League</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/bonucci-tro-ve-juventus-day-la-nha-cua-toi-176-192614.html\">Bonucci tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Juventus: \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5129","checkdouble":"193781"},{"date":"22:49 05/08","title":"U23 Th\u00e1i  Lan ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thua t\u1ee7i nh\u1ee5c t\u1ea1i Myanmar","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/trong-khi-viet-nam-thang-hoa-u23-thai-lan-tiep-tuc-thua-tui-nhuc-tai-myanmar.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>U23 Th\u00e1i Lan ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 ba li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu Alpine Cup 2018 sau tr\u1eadn thua 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 U23 Myanmar.</h2><h2>U23 Th\u00e1i Lan thua \u0111au ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Myanmar</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu Alpine Cup 2018 t\u1ea1i Myanmar, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i U23 Th\u00e1i Lan c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean tr\u00e1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng tham v\u1ecdng ban \u0111\u1ea7u, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 ch\u00f9a V\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t kh\u00e1 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Trong khi Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u0103ng hoa, U23 Th\u00e1i  Lan ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thua t\u1ee7i nh\u1ee5 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Trong khi Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u0103ng hoa, U23 Th\u00e1i  Lan ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thua t\u1ee7i nh\u1ee5 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/truc-tiep-u23-thai-lan-vs-u23-bahrain-15h30-ngay-1-81533108141.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>U23 Th\u00e1i Lan g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn \u1edf gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu\u00a0<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Alpine Cup 2018</span></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau c\u00e1c th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 2-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Bahrain, 2-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc U19 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i g\u1ee1 g\u1ea1c l\u1ea1i th\u1ec3 di\u1ec7n khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 U23 Myanmar \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n g\u1ed3m nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Th\u00e1i Lan m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf v\u1ec1 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m, \u0111\u1ec3 qua \u0111\u00f3 nh\u1eadn th\u00eam m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ec9 sau 11 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n U23 Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u00e3 hai l\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng, xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng m\u00e0 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u00e1o xanh m\u1eafc nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng. C\u00e1c b\u00e0n thua ch\u00f3ng v\u00e1nh n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e1ng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00f2n m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0o s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 \u00e1i c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i, tuy nhi\u00ean d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f9ng l\u00ean t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00f2ng m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n g\u1ee1, nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thua 1-2 chung cu\u1ed9c, U23 Th\u00e1i Lan ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ee9ng b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00e2y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o cho \u2018nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa voi chi\u1ebfn\u2019 tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u0103m nay, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng B c\u0169ng \u0110KV\u0110 U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 Uzbekistan, \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng 3 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 Qatar c\u00f9ng U23 Bangladesh. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9, vi\u1ec7c Th\u00e1i Lan b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i s\u1edbm ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 x\u1ea3y ra.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-khen-ngoi-2-cai-ten-xuat-sac-sau-tran-thang-oman-168-193795.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/hlv-park-hang-seo-khen-ngoi-2-cai-ten-xuat-sac-sau-tran-thang-oman.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-khen-ngoi-2-cai-ten-xuat-sac-sau-tran-thang-oman-168-193795.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo khen ng\u1ee3i 2 c\u00e1i t\u00ean xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Oman</span><br />\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi khen cho hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng v\u00e0 \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-oman-noi-gi-sau-sieu-pham-ghi-ban-cua-doan-van-hau-168-193794.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/hlv-oman-noi-gi-sau-sieu-pham-ghi-ban-cua-doan-van-hau.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-oman-noi-gi-sau-sieu-pham-ghi-ban-cua-doan-van-hau-168-193794.html\">HLV Oman n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu?</span><br />\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn, HLV Oman cho bi\u1ebft \u00f4ng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi pha ghi b\u00e0n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5128","checkdouble":"193796"},{"date":"23:05 05/08","title":"HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 ra h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/10/29/hlv-le-thuy-hai-chi-ra-han-che-cua-u23-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i kh\u00f3 nh\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc Oman, \u00f4ng L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t th\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo.</h2><h2>HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 ra h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba k\u1ebft th\u00fac t\u1ed1i 5/8, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i U23 Oman nh\u1edd b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 ra h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 ra h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/10/HLV-Le-Thuy-Hai-chi-ra-han-che-cua-U23-Viet-Nam-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i ch\u00ea \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh 2 c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t tr\u00ean Tri Th\u1ee9c Tr\u1ebb: \"\u0110\u00e3 g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh 2 th\u00ec ch\u00fang ta ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3, k\u00e9m qu\u00e1. \u0110\u1ec3 khen \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh 2 Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u00ec kh\u00f3 qu\u00e1. Ch\u00fang ta l\u1edfn v\u1edfn ph\u00eda ngo\u00e0i, b\u00ean trong th\u00ec ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u1ebf t\u1eafc. \u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh 2 n\u00ean ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t k\u00e9m. Ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p 1-2 t\u1eebng kho\u1ea3ng nh\u1ecf, nh\u00f3m nh\u1ecf th\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. 1-2 nh\u1ecbp \u0111\u1eadp t\u01b0\u1eddng th\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 th\u1ebf th\u00f4i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00fang ta xu\u1ed1ng bi\u00ean t\u1ea1t th\u00ec v\u00f4 \u00edch r\u1ed3i. H\u1ecd cao to h\u01a1n m\u00ecnh, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean To\u00e0n \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1eadp x\u00e0 nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng th\u00f4i. T\u1ea1t th\u00ec ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft, ch\u1ecdc v\u00e0o khe l\u1ed7 th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3. \u0110\u1eadp t\u01b0\u1eddng nhanh \u1edf trung l\u1ed9 c\u00f3 nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i h\u1ecfng. V\u00ec th\u1ebf r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady \u00f4ng H\u1ea3i \u2018l\u01a1\u2019 v\u1eabn d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi khen cho b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 SLNA l\u00e0 Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 Ph\u1ea1m Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh. V\u1ecb c\u1ef1u G\u0110KT Becamex B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng cho r\u1eb1ng V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p trong khi Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh l\u00e0 m\u1eabu h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 tin, d\u00e1m ch\u01a1i, d\u00e1m qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u1edf bi\u00ean.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i c\u0169ng cho r\u1eb1ng H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng l\u00e0 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t m\u00e0 HLV Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 U23 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng su\u1ea5t d\u1ef1 ASIAD cho 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ngo\u00e0i 23 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp t\u1edbi gi\u1eefa U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 U23 Uzbekistan, v\u1ecb HLV g\u1ed1c H\u00e0 \u0110\u00f4ng cho r\u1eb1ng HLV Park Hang Seo n\u00ean tung \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ra tr\u1eadn, v\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch r\u1ed3i. Nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng Park s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a ra \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng k\u00ec v\u1ecdng th\u1eafng thua g\u00ec \u1edf tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i n\u00e0y v\u00ec ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n v\u00e0 c\u0169ng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch r\u1ed3i. K\u00ec v\u1ecdng th\u00ec l\u00e0 c\u00e1c em s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t, ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p nhu\u1ea7n nhuy\u1ec5n, di chuy\u1ec3n h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, c\u1ef1 ly \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh... ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1\", HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i nh\u1eafn nh\u1ee7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c gi\u1eefa U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 U23 Uzbekistan s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra l\u00fac 19h30 ng\u00e0y 7/8 t\u1edbi. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a Palestine v\u00e0 Oman l\u00fac 16h30 c\u00f9ng ng\u00e0y.<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-khen-ngoi-2-cai-ten-xuat-sac-sau-tran-thang-oman-168-193795.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/hlv-park-hang-seo-khen-ngoi-2-cai-ten-xuat-sac-sau-tran-thang-oman.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-khen-ngoi-2-cai-ten-xuat-sac-sau-tran-thang-oman-168-193795.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo khen ng\u1ee3i 2 c\u00e1i t\u00ean xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Oman</span><br />\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi khen cho hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng v\u00e0 \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-oman-noi-gi-sau-sieu-pham-ghi-ban-cua-doan-van-hau-168-193794.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/hlv-oman-noi-gi-sau-sieu-pham-ghi-ban-cua-doan-van-hau.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-oman-noi-gi-sau-sieu-pham-ghi-ban-cua-doan-van-hau-168-193794.html\">HLV Oman n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu?</span><br />\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn, HLV Oman cho bi\u1ebft \u00f4ng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi pha ghi b\u00e0n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thua-palestine-hlv-u23-uzbekistan-thua-nhan-thua-kem-u23-viet-nam-168-193785.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/4/thua-palestine-hlv-u23-uzbekistan-thua-nhan-thua-kem-u23-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thua-palestine-hlv-u23-uzbekistan-thua-nhan-thua-kem-u23-viet-nam-168-193785.html\">Thua Palestine, HLV U23 Uzbekistan th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn thua k\u00e9m U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br />\r\nSau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-2 v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u nay tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine, HLV Nuraliev Dilshod th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i U23 Uzbekistan l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n c\u00f3 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n U23...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Highlight U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 1-0 U23 Oman<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span></strong><br />\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/5/Highlight-U23-Viet-Nam-vs-U23-Oman.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5127","checkdouble":"193797"},{"date":"23:33 05/08","title":"\u201cHi\u1ebfm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 V-League n\u00e0o l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/hiem-cau-thu-vleague-nao-lam-duoc-nhu-doan-van-hau.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Oman, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch H\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3ng HLV qu\u1ed1c gia, \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n S\u1ef9 Hi\u1ec3n cho r\u1eb1ng pha l\u00e0m b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t.</h2><h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, verdana, \" lucida=\"\">HLV Nguy\u1ec5n S\u1ef9 Hi\u1ec3n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a V\u0103n H\u1eadu</span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai \u1edf gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf c\u00fap Vinaphone 2018, \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Oman. V\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t s\u1eafm vai ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pha v\u1ea9y b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p b\u1eb1ng m\u00e1 ngo\u00e0i ch\u00e2n tr\u00e1i c\u1ee7a t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i B\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng \u0111i theo m\u1ed9t qu\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ea1o kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Oman ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Nguy\u1ec5n S\u1ef9 Hi\u1ec3n Hi\u1ebfm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Nguy\u1ec5n S\u1ef9 Hi\u1ec3n Hi\u1ebfm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/Thay-gi-sau-tran-U23-Viet-Nam-1-0-U23-Oman-hinh-anh-4.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi U23 Oman</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n S\u1ef9 Hi\u1ec3n, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang gi\u1eef ch\u1ee9c Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch H\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3ng HLV qu\u1ed1c gia \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u1eddi khen cho V\u0103n H\u1eadu.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ebfm c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o \u1edf V-League th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u1edf c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf ch\u00fang ta c\u0169ng kh\u00f3 th\u1ea5y pha v\u1ea9y m\u00e1 ngo\u00e0i ch\u00e2n tr\u00e1i \u0111i\u1ec7u ngh\u1ec7 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft c\u1ee7a V\u0103n H\u1eadu ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 may m\u1eafn&quot;, \u00f4ng Hi\u1ec3n cho bi\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n t\u1eebng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t th\u00eam v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo. \u00d4ng n\u00f3i: &ldquo;H\u00f4m nay HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 cho ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh 2. V\u00ec th\u1ebf trong su\u1ed1t hi\u1ec7p 1, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ecf ra thi\u1ebfu g\u1eafn k\u1ebft khi c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 \u00edt th\u1eddi gian t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi nhau, chuy\u1ec1n sai, di chuy\u1ec1n kh\u00f4ng g\u1ecdn. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cho \u0111\u1ebfn khi ch\u00fang ta thay 4, 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 V\u0103n To\u00e0n, V\u0103n H\u1eadu, \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh, \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng th\u00ec b\u1ed9 khung m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1, qua \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0103n b\u00e0n. T\u00f4i cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 HLV Park Hang Seo v\u00e0 BHL \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1eadt k\u1ef9 t\u1eebng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u1ed1t danh s\u00e1ch d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.&quot;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i n\u00e0y, U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. \u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p U23 Uzbekistan. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng mang theo \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t t\u1edbi Vi\u1ec7t Nam, vi\u1ec7c th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u1eefa l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 x\u1ea3y ra.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-le-thuy-hai-chi-ra-han-che-cua-u23-viet-nam-168-193797.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/10/29/hlv-le-thuy-hai-chi-ra-han-che-cua-u23-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-le-thuy-hai-chi-ra-han-che-cua-u23-viet-nam-168-193797.html\">HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 ra h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i kh\u00f3 nh\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc Oman, \u00f4ng L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t th\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/trong-khi-viet-nam-thang-hoa-u23-thai-lan-tiep-tuc-thua-tui-nhuc-tai-myanmar-168-193796.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/trong-khi-viet-nam-thang-hoa-u23-thai-lan-tiep-tuc-thua-tui-nhuc-tai-myanmar.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/trong-khi-viet-nam-thang-hoa-u23-thai-lan-tiep-tuc-thua-tui-nhuc-tai-myanmar-168-193796.html\">U23 Th\u00e1i  Lan ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thua t\u1ee7i nh\u1ee5c t\u1ea1i Myanmar</span><br>\r\nU23 Th\u00e1i Lan ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 ba li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu Alpine Cup 2018 sau tr\u1eadn thua 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 U23 Myanmar.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-khen-ngoi-2-cai-ten-xuat-sac-sau-tran-thang-oman-168-193795.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/hlv-park-hang-seo-khen-ngoi-2-cai-ten-xuat-sac-sau-tran-thang-oman.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-khen-ngoi-2-cai-ten-xuat-sac-sau-tran-thang-oman-168-193795.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo khen ng\u1ee3i 2 c\u00e1i t\u00ean xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Oman</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi khen cho hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng v\u00e0 \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-oman-noi-gi-sau-sieu-pham-ghi-ban-cua-doan-van-hau-168-193794.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/hlv-oman-noi-gi-sau-sieu-pham-ghi-ban-cua-doan-van-hau.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-oman-noi-gi-sau-sieu-pham-ghi-ban-cua-doan-van-hau-168-193794.html\">HLV Oman n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu?</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn, HLV Oman cho bi\u1ebft \u00f4ng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi pha ghi b\u00e0n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Highlight U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span></strong></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/5/Highlight-U23-Viet-Nam-vs-U23-Oman.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;&#10;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5126","checkdouble":"193801"},{"date":"00:52 06/08","title":"HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/9/hlv-phan-thanh-hung-noi-gi-ve-man-trinh-dien-cua-u23-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo.</h2><h2>HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e0 kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc ASIAD 2018 b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng c\u00fap Vinaphone 2018. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine hay Oman kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1edbm l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch m\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh cho ASIAD 2018.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/HLV-Phan-Thanh-Hung-noi-gi-ve-man-trinh-dien-cua-U23-Viet-Nam-hinh-anh.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua, c\u1ef1u HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110TQG, \u00f4ng Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng t\u00e2m s\u1ef1: \u201cV\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n m\u1edbi m\u1ebb, s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt thay \u0111\u1ed5i li\u00ean t\u1ee5c m\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1eabn gi\u1eef nh\u1ecbp l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 t\u00f4i quan t\u00e2m. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf HLV Park Hang-seo v\u00e0 \u00f4ng Lee Young-jin \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t huy \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. H\u1ecd hi\u1ec3u v\u00e0 gi\u00fap c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ef1 tin ch\u01a1i th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n \u0111ang d\u1eabn d\u1eaft CLB Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 vi\u1ec7c th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m hai \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng Park \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hai b\u00e0i to\u00e1n v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u00edch nghi c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o ASIAD.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i AFF Cup. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cH\u00f9ng D\u0169ng l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng Park Hang-seo. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi ba c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean U23 kh\u00e1c, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 l\u1ebd s\u1ebd c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 khung c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u1edf k\u1ef3 AFF Cup 2018 cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m\u201d, HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng n\u00f3i th\u00eam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Uzbekistan s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h30 ng\u00e0y 7/8 t\u1edbi t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-le-thuy-hai-chi-ra-han-che-cua-u23-viet-nam-168-193797.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/10/29/hlv-le-thuy-hai-chi-ra-han-che-cua-u23-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-le-thuy-hai-chi-ra-han-che-cua-u23-viet-nam-168-193797.html\">HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 ra h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i kh\u00f3 nh\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc Oman, \u00f4ng L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t th\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-khen-ngoi-2-cai-ten-xuat-sac-sau-tran-thang-oman-168-193795.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/hlv-park-hang-seo-khen-ngoi-2-cai-ten-xuat-sac-sau-tran-thang-oman.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-khen-ngoi-2-cai-ten-xuat-sac-sau-tran-thang-oman-168-193795.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo khen ng\u1ee3i 2 c\u00e1i t\u00ean xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Oman</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi khen cho hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng v\u00e0 \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-oman-noi-gi-sau-sieu-pham-ghi-ban-cua-doan-van-hau-168-193794.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/hlv-oman-noi-gi-sau-sieu-pham-ghi-ban-cua-doan-van-hau.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-oman-noi-gi-sau-sieu-pham-ghi-ban-cua-doan-van-hau-168-193794.html\">HLV Oman n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu?</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn, HLV Oman cho bi\u1ebft \u00f4ng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi pha ghi b\u00e0n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Highlight U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Oman</strong><span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/5/Highlight-U23-Viet-Nam-vs-U23-Oman.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; line-height: 115%; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5125","checkdouble":"193807"},{"date":"02:37 06/08","title":"L\u00fd do U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1edbm ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/5/ly-do-u23-viet-nam-da-hai-tran-da-chinh-thuc-vo-dich.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi hai th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine v\u00e0 Oman, \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap c\u00f9ng ph\u1ea7n th\u01b0\u1edfng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 20 ngh\u00ecn \u0111\u00f4 la cho m\u00ecnh. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2u l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1edbm v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch?</h2><h2>L\u00fd do U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch s\u1edbm 1 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u00fd do U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch s\u1edbm 1 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u00fd do U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch s\u1edbm 1 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/HLV-Phan-Thanh-Hung-noi-gi-ve-man-trinh-dien-cua-U23-Viet-Nam-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Oman</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf c\u00fap Vinaphone 2018, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0u ti\u00ean so s\u00e1nh tr\u01b0\u1edbc so v\u1edbi hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng b\u1ea1i trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec3m nhau. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Palestine \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean n\u00ean n\u1ebfu U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 thua Uzbekistan \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f2n Palestine h\u1ea1 Oman, khi \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea3 Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u1eabn Palestine s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng c\u00f3 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m, nh\u01b0ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch do h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea3 Oman v\u00e0 Uzbekistan cho t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1edbm v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, d\u00f9 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch n\u00e0y, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i, HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ra g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Li\u00ean quan t\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf c\u00fap Vinaphone 2018, \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd l\u0129nh ph\u1ea7n th\u01b0\u1edfng cho \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch l\u00e0 20.000 \u0111\u00f4la M\u1ef9. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n th\u01b0\u1edfng ri\u00eang c\u1ee7a VFF, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn tr\u01b0\u1edbc ASIAD. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nHy v\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd thi \u0111\u1ea5u quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m h\u01a1n n\u1eefa v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c.<br />\r\n\u00a0</p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/5/Highlight-U23-Viet-Nam-vs-U23-Oman.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hiem-cau-thu-vleague-nao-lam-duoc-nhu-doan-van-hau-168-193801.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/5/hiem-cau-thu-vleague-nao-lam-duoc-nhu-doan-van-hau.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hiem-cau-thu-vleague-nao-lam-duoc-nhu-doan-van-hau-168-193801.html\">\u201cHi\u1ebfm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 V-League n\u00e0o l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu\u201d</span><br />\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Oman, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch H\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3ng HLV qu\u1ed1c gia, \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n S\u1ef9 Hi\u1ec3n cho r\u1eb1ng pha l\u00e0m b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb7c...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-phan-thanh-hung-noi-gi-ve-man-trinh-dien-cua-u23-viet-nam-168-193807.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/9/hlv-phan-thanh-hung-noi-gi-ve-man-trinh-dien-cua-u23-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-phan-thanh-hung-noi-gi-ve-man-trinh-dien-cua-u23-viet-nam-168-193807.html\">HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</span><br />\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-le-thuy-hai-chi-ra-han-che-cua-u23-viet-nam-168-193797.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/10/29/hlv-le-thuy-hai-chi-ra-han-che-cua-u23-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-le-thuy-hai-chi-ra-han-che-cua-u23-viet-nam-168-193797.html\">HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9 ra h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br />\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i kh\u00f3 nh\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc Oman, \u00f4ng L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t th\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5124","checkdouble":"193812"},{"date":"20:18 05/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 5/8: B\u1eb1ng ch\u1ee9ng cho th\u1ea5y Martial s\u1eafp r\u1eddi MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-58-bang-chung-cho-thay-martial-sap-roi-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 5/8.</h2><h2>Everton quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 MU</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo t\u1edd TeamTalk, Everton s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Smalling ho\u1eb7c Lindelof n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Rojo. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng Merseyside r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng mua \u0111\u1ee9t Smalling ho\u1eb7c m\u01b0\u1ee3n Lindelof v\u1edbi th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n<h2>Cillessen s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Barca</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Ernesto Valverde hy v\u1ecdng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Jasper Cillessen s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Barcelona sau khi anh ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u kh\u00e1 \u00fap m\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi AC Milan t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i ICC, Cilessen \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi &ldquo;t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft&rdquo; khi d\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. Nh\u01b0ng HLV Valverde c\u00f4ng khai b\u00e0y t\u1ecf hy v\u1ecdng Cilessen s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Camp Nou v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi Ter Stegen.</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb cho Ramsey</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Daily Express kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Aaron Ramsye t\u1eeb Arsenal. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Arsenal v\u00e0 Chelsea hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Liverpool c\u0169ng c\u00f3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Ramsey nh\u01b0ng Chelsea th\u00ec l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn chi ti\u1ebft h\u01a1n kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u sau khi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Jack Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa.</div>\r\n<h2>Martial kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cao r\u1eddi MU\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 58 Martial s\u1eafp r\u1eddi MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 58 Martial s\u1eafp r\u1eddi MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-hom-nay-ngay-38,-tin-chuyen-nhuong-he-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 5/8:&nbsp;Martial b\u1ecb b\u1ecf r\u01a1i trong tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Manchester Evening News kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Martial \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb b\u1ecf l\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Man United d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi Bayern Munich. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd s\u1edbm r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n Old Trafford sau khi ch\u1ecdc gi\u1eadn HLV Jose Mourinho. Vi\u1ec7c anh b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tham d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi Bayern c\u00e0ng l\u00e0m tin \u0111\u1ed3n n\u00e0y c\u00f3 c\u01a1 s\u1edf h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<h2>Giroud ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Marseille</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Olivier Giroud m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i vi\u1ec7c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Marseille ngay h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, trong \u00edt ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi, Giroud s\u1ebd c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p v\u1edbi HLV Maurizio Sarri \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m r\u00f5 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang ch\u01a1i \u1edf Ligue 1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u01b0a Giroud tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Arsenal kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y m\u1eb7n m\u00e0 v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ligue 1 v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-58-lo-muc-gia-de-mu-so-huu-alderweireld-184-193743.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 5/8: L\u1ed9 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 M.U s\u1edf h\u1eefu Alderweireld</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-0408-day-chi-tiet-hop-dong-mu-sap-ky-voi-yerry-mina-184-193723.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 04/08: \u0110\u00e2y! Chi ti\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng MU s\u1eafp k\u00fd v\u1edbi Yerry Mina</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Bongda24h.vn (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5123","checkdouble":"193786"},{"date":"21:51 05/08","title":"Bayern Munich 1-0 MU: \u0110\u00e1 giao h\u1eefu nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e1 th\u1eadt, \"Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\" thua ... c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/5/bayern-munich-vs-mu-tran-dau-giao-huu-clb-he-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eadp d\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester v\u1eabn th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u00f5 t\u00e2m l\u00fd s\u1ee3 thua khi ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng trong ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn th\u1eddi gian v\u00e0 h\u1ecda ho\u1eb1n l\u1eafm m\u1edbi t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng. B\u1edfi v\u1eady, r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, H\u00f9m x\u00e1m m\u1edbi t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t nh\u1edd c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Javi Martinez trong m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh.</h2><h2>T\u1ed4NG H\u1ee2P: BAYERN MUNICH 1-0 MU\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/8/6/hx3zEr.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<p><br>\r\nMan United thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n m\u00f9a H\u00e8 n\u0103m nay. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn giao  h\u1eefu cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng g\u1eb7p Bayern tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t \u0110\u1ee9c, th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 h\u00f2a 3, thua 1 v\u00e0  th\u1eafng 1. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Real Madrid 2-1 t\u1ea1i ICC  2018 trong m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn m\u00e0 \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Jose Mourinho d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 2  b\u00e0n trong hi\u1ec7p 1 nh\u1edd c\u00e1c pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Alexis Sanchez v\u00e0 Ander Herrera. Sau  \u0111\u00e2y kho\u1ea3ng 1 tu\u1ea7n, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn khai m\u1ea1c Premier League 2018/19 g\u1eb7p  Leicester City.</p>\r\n<p>Bayern Munich c\u0169ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u  ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ICC 2018 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c PSG 3-1, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u00e0u truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c  b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 khi l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ec3 thua Juventus 0-2 v\u00e0 thua Man City 2-3. Qua 3  tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3, Bayern Munich cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t \u1ed5n trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 khi kh\u00f4ng tr\u1eadn n\u00e0o  h\u1ecd gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi. Trong \u0111\u00f3, \u1edf tr\u1eadn thua 2-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City, c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a  \u00f4ng Kovac th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n d\u1eabn 2 b\u00e0n t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm, nh\u01b0ng sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ghi  3 b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1eadt ng\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Bayern Munich vs MU tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018 \u0111\u00eam nay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Bayern Munich vs MU tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018 \u0111\u00eam nay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/Truc-tiep-Bayern-Munich-vs-MU-tran-dau-giao-huu-he-2018-dem-nay-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">De Gea l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a M.U v\u1edbi v\u00e0i t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ee9u thua xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nDo l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1eadn k\u1ec1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi v\u00e0 di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u00e2u  M\u1ef9 xa x\u00f4i n\u00ean hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tung ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 so v\u1edbi khi  c\u00f9ng tham d\u1ef1 ICC 2018 b\u1edfi c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao v\u1eeba tham d\u1ef1 World Cup  2018 m\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bao l\u00e2u do \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i  th\u00eam. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, b\u00ean ph\u00eda ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Bayern th\u00ec s\u1ed1 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 \u0110\u1ee9c g\u1ed3m th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Neuer,  c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 Sule vs Hummels, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh Kimmich c\u00f9ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Muller \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n  t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u. V\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n Man United th\u00ec Lindelof \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p v\u1edbi Bailly  c\u00f2n tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, Rashford \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng cho Mata v\u00e0 Alexis Sanchez. T\u00e2n  binh Fred ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i sau ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i khai cu\u1ed9c khi hai b\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng tri\u1ec3n  khai t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a nhau. C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 v\u1edbi c\u00fa  \u0111\u1eb7t l\u00f2ng c\u1ee7a Thiago t\u1eeb ngo\u00e0i v\u1ea1ch 16m50 v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh De Gea \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed5 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee9u  thua cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh. Sau kho\u1ea3ng h\u01a1n ch\u1ee5c ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u, th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn d\u1ea7n r\u01a1i  v\u00e0o tay Bayern song ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 \u1edf m\u1ee9c trung b\u00ecnh th\u1ea5p n\u00ean  ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y ra nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Man Utd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00fat 17, nguy hi\u1ec3m ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n t\u1eeb b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba \"Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\" v\u00e0 l\u1ea7n  n\u00e0y De Gea lai ph\u1ea3i ra tay ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u1ee9ng c\u00fa s\u00fat ch\u00ecm uy l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Gnarby, sao tr\u1ebb sinh  n\u0103m 1996 t\u1eebng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Arsenal. Tuy v\u1eady, tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, si\u00eau th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n  ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 trong hi\u1ec7p 1 b\u1edfi ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \"H\u00f9m  x\u00e1m\" \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng qua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u00e0 h\u1ecda ho\u1eb1n l\u1eafm m\u1edbi c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng  t\u00ecm tr\u00fang m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bayern Munich 1-0 MU \u0110\u00e1 giao h\u1eefu nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e1 th\u1eadt, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf thua  c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Bayern Munich 1-0 MU \u0110\u00e1 giao h\u1eefu nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e1 th\u1eadt, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf thua  c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/Bayern-Munich-1-0-MU-Da-giao-huu-nhu-da-that,-Quy-do-thua--co-ke-hoach-hinh-anh-2.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">D\u00f9 c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u01b0 Alexis Sanchez song c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn, M.U kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u1ea5y n\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o ra h\u1ed3n b\u1edfi \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 ch\u0103m ch\u0103m ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00fat 39, c\u00fa s\u00fat t\u1eeb ngo\u00e0i v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m c\u1ee7a Ribery \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea1m v\u00e0o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ander Herrera \u0111\u1ed5i  h\u01b0\u1edbng song De Gea v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed5 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea9y b\u00f3ng ra ngo\u00e0i.  \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7p 1. Sau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 gi\u1ea3i lao, Bayern  Munich \u0111\u00e3 thay v\u00e0i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u00ean s\u00e2n trong khi Mourinho quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i  h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh khi Bailly c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u b\u1ecb \u0111au  (Smalling v\u00e0o thay).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7p 1, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u00f3 tay tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ki\u00ean  c\u1ed1, nhi\u1ec1u l\u1edbp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1ng ra tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n De Gea. D\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu v\u00f4  th\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00f4 ph\u1ea1t song Mourinho v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t coi tr\u1ecdng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 khi \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng tri\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea5u  ph\u00e1p th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng \u01b0a th\u00edch. Ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh M.U \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eadp trung b\u00ean ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0  v\u00e0 k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t h\u1eddi h\u1ee3t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy v\u1eady, c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac m\u00e0nh l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a M.U ph\u1ea3i rung l\u00ean. Ph\u00fat 59, t\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t  g\u00f3c, Javi Martinez \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eadt r\u1ea5t cao \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c De Gea. D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n  thua song \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester ch\u1eb3ng cho th\u1ea5y d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u g\u00ec mu\u1ed1n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a. Th\u1eadm  ch\u00ed, HLV Mourinho c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0a hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng (Mata, Rashford) ra ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i v\u00e0  thay th\u1ebf cho h\u1ecd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ... ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 (McTominay) c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t ... h\u1eadu v\u1ec7  \u0111\u00edch th\u1ef1c (Fosu-Mensah).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ebf l\u00e0, ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng n\u00e0o xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n. Man United v\u1eabn ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn  b\u1ecb d\u1ed3n \u00e9p v\u00e0 v\u00e2y h\u00e3m cho \u0111\u1ebfn ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i m\u00e3n cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 v\u00f9ng l\u00ean t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng  m\u00e1u l\u1eeda h\u00f2ng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a. Ch\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i h\u1ecd s\u1ee3 hay \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh k\u00e9m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00e0 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n  Mourinho th\u00edch th\u1ebf. Ph\u00fat 81, Kingsley Coman c\u0103ng ngang thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i v\u00e0o ph\u00eda trong  cho Leon Goretzka, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 \u0110\u1ee9c m\u1edbi gia nh\u1eadp Bayern h\u00e8 n\u00e0y t\u1eeb Schalke v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n  v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 r\u1ea3nh ch\u00e2n s\u00fat tr\u00e1i ph\u00e1, \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng \u0111i ch\u1ec7ch c\u1ea7u m\u00f4n trong gang  t\u1ea5c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00fat 86, m\u00e0nh l\u01b0\u1edbi Man Utd \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i rung l\u00ean sau c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Robben nh\u01b0ng  tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i bi\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea5t c\u1edd b\u00e1o l\u1ed7i vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c. 1-0 l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 chung cu\u1ed9c  c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, Man United \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 \u1ea3m \u0111\u1ea1m b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t  b\u1ea1i n\u1eefa. \u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 \u00fd \u0111\u1ed3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a Jose Mourinho. Thay  v\u00ec cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i bung s\u1ee9c ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y th\u00eam  \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi th\u00ec \u00f4ng l\u1ea1i nghi\u00eam t\u00fac m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch th\u00e1i qu\u00e1 khi \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng  tri\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng nh\u00e0m ch\u00e1n, bu\u1ed3n ng\u1ee7 d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng.  Ph\u1ea3i ch\u0103ng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1m b\u00e1o  kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0nh v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 c\u1ee7a Manchester United.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH THI \u0110\u1ea4U<br>\r\nBayern Munich:</strong> Neuer, Sule, Hummels, Alaba (Bernat 56'), Kimmich, Thiago Alcantara,  Ribery (Goretzka 46'), Javi Martinez, Robben, Gnabry, Muller (Lewandowski 46')<br>\r\n<strong>Man Utd:</strong> De Gea (Lee Grant 77'), Darmian (Phil Jones 65'), Bailly (Smalling 48'), Lindelof, Shaw (Mitchell 77'), Herrera (Garner 80'),  Fred (Tahith Chong 77'), Andres Pereira, Mata (McTominay 65'), Rashford (Fosu-Mensah\u00a0 65'), Alexis Sanchez<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f4ng Minh (TTVN)\r\n<p>\u00a0</p>\r\n<p>\u00a0</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5122","checkdouble":"193792"},{"date":"20:34 05/08","title":"HLV Valverde mu\u1ed1n \u201cd\u1ef1 b\u1ecb h\u1ea1ng sang\u201d \u1edf l\u1ea1i Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/5/hlv-valverde-muon-cillessen-o-lai-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Valverde mu\u1ed1n Cillessen \u1edf l\u1ea1i Barca. Thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Blaugrana mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c n\u1eb7ng d\u00e0nh cho th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 Marc-Andre ter Stegen.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Cillessen kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJasper Cillessen gia nh\u1eadp Barcelona t\u1eeb Ajax n\u0103m 2016 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 13 tri\u1ec7u Euro. 2 n\u0103m tr\u00f4i qua, anh m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 4 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng t\u1ea1i La Liga v\u00e0 Champions League. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Marc-Andre ter Stegen trong khung g\u1ed7, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u00fap Nh\u00e0 vua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup, Cillessen \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft tr\u1ecdn 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u1edbi AS Roma v\u00e0 Tottenham. Nh\u01b0ng khi Ter Stegen tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u1eadu World Cup 2018, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t hi\u1ec7p tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 sau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Valverde mu\u1ed1n Cillessen \u1edf l\u1ea1i Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Valverde mu\u1ed1n Cillessen \u1edf l\u1ea1i Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/7/HLV-Valverde-muon-Cillessen-o-lai-Barca-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">C\u00f3 tin Cillessen s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Barcelona h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00e8 n\u00e0y, \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin Cillessen c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Barca. Chelsea nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n Barca ph\u00f2ng tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Thibaut Courtois chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Real Madrid.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Valverde l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca m\u1edbi th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc AC Milan t\u1ea1i International Champions Cup. Sau tr\u1eadn, ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecfi Cillessen v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Anh ch\u1ec9 tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n r\u1eb1ng: \u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Cillessen\" title=\"thu mon Cillessen\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/hlv-valverde-muon-cillessen-o-lai-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV Valverde mu\u1ed1n Cillessen \u1edf l\u1ea1i Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nErnesto Valverde th\u00ec tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng h\u01a1n. HLV Valverde mu\u1ed1n Cillessen \u1edf l\u1ea1i Barca v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh gi\u00e0u s\u1ee9c n\u1eb7ng cho Ter Stegen. \u201cK\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 c\u00f3 2 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. Hi\u1ec7n ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 Ter Stegen v\u00e0 Cillessen\u201d, \u00f4ng n\u00f3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00fang l\u00e0 Cillessen kh\u00f4ng ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u nh\u01b0 Ter Stegen. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y bi\u1ebft t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 g\u00ec. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi t\u00ednh chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a Cillessen. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y.\u201d<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barcelona tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-valverde-noi-gi-truoc-tin-don-barca-quan-tam-pogba-180-193728.html\">HLV Valverde n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n Barca quan t\u00e2m Pogba?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chi-120-trieu-euro-ac-milan-tinh-vuot-mat-mu-vu-pogba-serbia-172-193722.html\">Chi 120 tri\u1ec7u euro, AC Milan t\u00ednh v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t MU v\u1ee5 Pogba Serbia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/cuc-nong-pogba-da-chon-xong-so-ao-o-barca-180-193721.html\">C\u1ef1c n\u00f3ng: Pogba \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn xong s\u1ed1 \u00e1o \u1edf Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/tro-thanh-dong-doi-messi-vidal-len-tieng-cam-on-hum-xam-180-193716.html\">Tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Messi, Vidal l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3m \u01a1n H\u00f9m x\u00e1m</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-chinh-thuc-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-sao-khung-bayern-munich-180-193675.html\">Barca CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng sao kh\u1ee7ng Bayern Munich</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5121","checkdouble":"193784"}]}